<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 18:07:45 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的内容 – 第 135 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-135/0000018d-bd37-dc8c-a3df-ff37f8020000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡政府一致通过决议，拒绝国际单方面承认巴勒斯坦国 ■ 甘茨：如果斋月期间不释放哈马斯扣押的人质，以色列将扩大对拉法的地面行动 ■ 欧盟消息人士称，他们帮助将原本为以色列人质提供的药品带入加沙 ■ 巴西卢拉总统将以色列在加沙的行动与大屠杀进行比较 ■ 这是战争 135 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 17:30:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-135/0000018d-bd37-dc8c-a3df-ff37f8020000</guid></item><item><title>国际法院应联合国要求考虑以色列控制西岸和东耶路撒冷的合法性</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/icj-to-consider-legality-of-israels-control-over-west-bank-and-east-jerusalem/0000018d-bcd4-dd5e-a59d-fdf6fb5a0000</link><description>联合国大会要求海牙联合国最高法院就这一问题提供不具约束力的法律意见，但预计许多国家将予以高度重视</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 16:37:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/icj-to-consider-legality-of-israels-control-over-west-bank-and-east-jerusalem/0000018d-bcd4-dd5e-a59d-fdf6fb5a0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡抨击巴西总统卢拉将以色列在加沙的行动与“希特勒的种族灭绝”相比较</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/netanyahu-slams-brazils-lula-for-comparing-israels-gaza-actions-to-hitlers-genocide/0000018d-bcaa-df10-a99f-bffb0da90000</link><description>巴西总统说：“加沙地带和巴勒斯坦人民所发生的事情在任何其他历史时刻都不存在。”事实上，当希特勒决定屠杀犹太人时，它就已经存在了。以色列宣布将传唤巴西大使进行谴责</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 16:02:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/netanyahu-slams-brazils-lula-for-comparing-israels-gaza-actions-to-hitlers-genocide/0000018d-bcaa-df10-a99f-bffb0da90000</guid></item><item><title>英国工党领袖斯塔默呼吁以色列和哈马斯之间持久停火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/u-k-labour-leader-calls-for-lasting-gaza-cease-fire-says-rafah-offensive-cannot-happen/0000018d-bcc1-df10-a99f-bff321cf0000</link><description>斯塔默表示，“即使在最可怕的情况下，两国解决方案也必须重新回到桌面上”，同时强调以色列即将对拉法发动的进攻“不可能发生”</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 15:50:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/u-k-labour-leader-calls-for-lasting-gaza-cease-fire-says-rafah-offensive-cannot-happen/0000018d-bcc1-df10-a99f-bff321cf0000</guid></item><item><title>“她们带着故事而来”：战时以色列助产士接生、支持和希望</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-haven-of-sanity-the-israeli-midwives-delivering-babies-and-hope-during-wartime/0000018d-bc74-dc8c-a3df-fe7591ea0000</link><description>随着越来越多的以色列妇女分娩，而她们的伴侣却在前线，甚至更糟，助产士自愿帮助她们做的不仅仅是呼吸练习。一位人士表示，“有时你必须提醒他们自己怀孕了——他们需要关注这一点”</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 15:48:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-haven-of-sanity-the-israeli-midwives-delivering-babies-and-hope-during-wartime/0000018d-bc74-dc8c-a3df-fe7591ea0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府一致拒绝国际社会单方面承认巴勒斯坦国</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-govt-unanimously-rejects-unilateral-intl-recognition-of-palestinian-state/0000018d-bcbe-dd5e-a59d-fdbe1d020000</link><description>总理告诉内阁，此举是在国际社会试图“单方面将巴勒斯坦国强加于以色列”之际做出的。该决议确定任何永久性安排“只能通过不设先决条件的直接谈判来实现”</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 15:32:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-govt-unanimously-rejects-unilateral-intl-recognition-of-palestinian-state/0000018d-bcbe-dd5e-a59d-fdbe1d020000</guid></item><item><title>在美国的限制下，受制裁的以色列定居者共同拥有的公司在其兄弟名下注册</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/company-of-sanctioned-israeli-settler-registered-under-his-brother-amid-restrictions/0000018d-bc42-dc8c-a3df-fe7719280000</link><description>美国对约旦河西岸活动家伊农·莱维实施制裁后，他表示公司银行账户已被冻结，而他的兄弟则否认制裁后登记了所有权变更</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 14:35:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/company-of-sanctioned-israeli-settler-registered-under-his-brother-amid-restrictions/0000018d-bc42-dc8c-a3df-fe7719280000</guid></item><item><title>在花费数年时间使以色列两极分化之后，内塔尼亚胡将团结作为武器来对抗异见</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/after-spending-years-polarizing-israel-netanyahu-uses-unity-as-a-weapon-against-dissent/0000018d-bc12-df10-a99f-bff397fe0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡曾经证明，对他来说，战争为另一场政治运动提供了一个平台，其特点是所有熟悉的特征：谎言、煽动、煽动激情和转移注意力</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 13:26:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/after-spending-years-polarizing-israel-netanyahu-uses-unity-as-a-weapon-against-dissent/0000018d-bc12-df10-a99f-bff397fe0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列教育部长取消除“英雄主义”之外的所有以色列奖奖项类别</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-education-minister-cancels-all-israel-prize-awards-categories-except-for-heroism/0000018d-bbfe-dd5e-a59d-fffe21930000</link><description>今年的以色列奖将不会颁发传统的人文、科学和文化类别，而只会颁发一个类别，其中六名获奖者“在 10 月 7 日发生的可怕危机后为国家的复苏做出了贡献”</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 12:52:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-education-minister-cancels-all-israel-prize-awards-categories-except-for-heroism/0000018d-bbfe-dd5e-a59d-fffe21930000</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔的赚钱机器为其全球影响力铺平道路</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/qatars-money-machine-smooths-its-path-to-global-influence/0000018d-ad18-d30f-a39f-ff797e3b0000</link><description>这个小酋长国为包括哈马斯在内的伊斯兰恐怖组织提供资金，并控制了美国在核技术、网络安全和人工智能方面的战略资产。我们是否应该担心这一切最终都会落入伊朗手中？</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 12:44:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/qatars-money-machine-smooths-its-path-to-global-influence/0000018d-ad18-d30f-a39f-ff797e3b0000</guid></item><item><title>无人机的黄金：大规模泄漏揭示了俄罗斯的伊朗沙赫德项目</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-02-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/gold-for-drones-massive-leak-reveals-the-iranian-shahed-project-in-russia/0000018d-bb85-dd5e-a59d-ffb729890000</link><description>文件揭示了售价 20 万美元的 Shahed 136 如何成为俄罗斯在乌克兰武库中的致命武器，以及先进型号的外观</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 12:10:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-02-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/gold-for-drones-massive-leak-reveals-the-iranian-shahed-project-in-russia/0000018d-bb85-dd5e-a59d-ffb729890000</guid></item><item><title>古生物学家发现古代鱼类有鼻孔：可能是第一种呼吸空气的动物</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-02-18/ty-article/paleontologists-find-ancient-fish-with-nostrils-may-have-been-first-animal-to-breathe-air/0000018d-bba4-dd5e-a59d-ffb637550000</link><description>Harajicadectes 生活在 3.8 亿年前的澳大利亚，有鳍，没有腿，头上有孔，显然是作为气孔</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 10:44:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-02-18/ty-article/paleontologists-find-ancient-fish-with-nostrils-may-have-been-first-animal-to-breathe-air/0000018d-bba4-dd5e-a59d-ffb637550000</guid></item><item><title>随着未来的正常化，以色列也愿意冒现有和平协议的风险</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/along-with-future-normalization-israel-is-also-willing-to-risk-existing-peace-deals/0000018d-bb3c-dc8c-a3df-fb3d15130000</link><description>当国际社会厌倦了等待加沙战争的“第二天”时，越来越多的国家开始支持建立巴勒斯坦国，而内塔尼亚胡却忙着人云亦云的空话。</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 09:44:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/along-with-future-normalization-israel-is-also-willing-to-risk-existing-peace-deals/0000018d-bb3c-dc8c-a3df-fb3d15130000</guid></item><item><title>尽管有言论，内塔尼亚胡和以色列军队都不愿意在拉法行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/despite-talk-neither-netanyahu-nor-the-israeli-army-are-eager-to-operate-in-rafah/0000018d-b8ed-dc8c-a3df-fafdd5d20000</link><description>随着人质解救时间的临近，内塔尼亚胡的立场变得更强硬，以加大对哈马斯的压力，而哈马斯在加沙境外的领导人伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚则要求不启动，达成协议的机会似乎正在减少</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 04:52:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/despite-talk-neither-netanyahu-nor-the-israeli-army-are-eager-to-operate-in-rafah/0000018d-b8ed-dc8c-a3df-fafdd5d20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列将在斋月期间限制阿拉伯-以色列人进入圣殿山/阿克萨清真寺</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article-live/algeria-submits-gaza-cease-fire-proposal-to-un-u-s-says-will-oppose/0000018d-ba05-dc8c-a3df-fa35ad830000</link><description>约旦FM 告诉BBC 内塔尼亚胡“决心继续在加沙进行更多杀戮、更多破坏” ■ 巴西总统将以色列在加沙的行动比作大屠杀；内塔尼亚胡召见巴西大使进行谴责 ■ 巴勒斯坦总理称巴勒斯坦权力机构已准备好与哈马斯接触，各派系将于下周在莫斯科举行会议 ■ 巴勒斯坦卫生部表示，两名巴勒斯坦人在约旦河西岸被以色列国防军炮火打死</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 03:50:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article-live/algeria-submits-gaza-cease-fire-proposal-to-un-u-s-says-will-oppose/0000018d-ba05-dc8c-a3df-fa35ad830000</guid></item><item><title>拉法突袭中人质获释：“并非所有人质都能在英勇行动中获救”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-17/ty-article/.premium/hostages-freed-in-rafah-raid-not-all-hostages-can-be-rescued-in-heroic-operations/0000018d-b8c5-dd5e-a59d-fdf7f6480000</link><description>数千名以色列人聚集在特拉维夫，支持在加沙被扣押的人质亲属，他们敦促内塔尼亚胡派代表团参加开罗会谈，并指责政府抛弃了他们的亲人</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Feb 2024 21:03:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-17/ty-article/.premium/hostages-freed-in-rafah-raid-not-all-hostages-can-be-rescued-in-heroic-operations/0000018d-b8c5-dd5e-a59d-fdf7f6480000</guid></item><item><title>道路封锁、与警察发生冲突：以色列各地数千人集会反对内塔尼亚胡政府</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-17/ty-article/.premium/blocked-roads-clashes-with-police-thousands-rally-against-netanyahus-government/0000018d-b8ae-dc8c-a3df-fabf5a0d0000</link><description>特拉维夫、耶路撒冷、海法、贝尔谢巴和凯撒利亚的数千名反政府示威者呼吁提前选举并罢免总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Feb 2024 20:38:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-17/ty-article/.premium/blocked-roads-clashes-with-police-thousands-rally-against-netanyahus-government/0000018d-b8ae-dc8c-a3df-fabf5a0d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国家安全顾问表示，内塔尼亚胡本周将尝试制定加沙“事后”计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-17/ty-article/netanyahu-to-try-to-formulate-day-after-plan-for-gaza-says-national-security-adviser/0000018d-b89e-dc8c-a3df-fabf31c80000</link><description>以色列国家安全顾问查奇·哈内格比 (Tzachi Hanegbi) 在接受 Kan 11 采访时表示，“我们没有兴趣管理加沙 220 万巴勒斯坦人的生活”</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Feb 2024 20:02:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-17/ty-article/netanyahu-to-try-to-formulate-day-after-plan-for-gaza-says-national-security-adviser/0000018d-b89e-dc8c-a3df-fabf31c80000</guid></item><item><title>随着以色列发动战争，亲巴勒斯坦的抗议活动席卷了艺术界</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-02-17/ty-article/.premium/the-pro-palestine-protests-taking-over-the-art-world-as-israel-wages-war/0000018d-ad41-dc8c-a3df-ff7582180000</link><description>随着毁灭性的加沙战争进入第四个月，不同类型的战斗正在世界各地的文化机构蔓延——包括柏林的汉堡火车站、纽约的现代艺术博物馆、伦敦的苏荷剧院和大英博物馆</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Feb 2024 19:12:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-02-17/ty-article/.premium/the-pro-palestine-protests-taking-over-the-art-world-as-israel-wages-war/0000018d-ad41-dc8c-a3df-ff7582180000</guid></item><item><title>安全消息人士称，以色列警方对阻止针对加沙援助的抗议活动持谨慎态度</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-wary-of-blocking-protests-against-gaza-aid-security-sources-say/0000018d-b83b-dc8c-a3df-fa3fd5f40000</link><description>消息人士称，根据国家安全部长本-格维尔的命令，南区警察局长缺席了与以色列陆军参谋长就此事举行的会议</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Feb 2024 18:36:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-wary-of-blocking-protests-against-gaza-aid-security-sources-say/0000018d-b83b-dc8c-a3df-fa3fd5f40000</guid></item></channel></rss>